# Tabocalypse PM board (Projocalypse)

Submodule: `packages/projocalypse`. **Package key:** `tabocalypse-roadmap` in `.projocalypse/workspace.json`.

## Source of truth (git on `master`)

| What | Path |
|------|------|
| Plan checkboxes | `doc/PLAN/ROADMAP-PM-BOARD.md` (`pm:PM-T###` ids) |
| Candidate options (pre-approval) | `doc/PLAN/ROADMAP.md` |
| Team sync JSON | `.projocalypse/pending/tabocalypse-roadmap.json` — **commit when changed** |
| Registry + column names | `.projocalypse/workspace.json` |

## Mandatory sync when task status changes

Whenever a roadmap task moves open ↔ done, changes priority column, or is added/removed:

1. Update `ROADMAP-PM-BOARD.md` (`[x]` / `[ ]`, `pm:section=…`, `pm:section=Done` when complete).
2. Run **`pnpm pm:sync`**.
3. Commit plan + pending JSON in the same PR as the status change.

## Daily / after pull

```bash
git pull origin master
pnpm pm:sync
pnpm pm:stale
pnpm pm:board
```

## First-time

```bash
pnpm pm:setup
pnpm pm:board
```

See [doc/PLAN/PROJOCALYPSE.md](../../doc/PLAN/PROJOCALYPSE.md).

## Agents

- **`tabocalypse-pm-board`** skill — full sync loop
